snippet.title: Gran Turismo 1
snippet.description:
Gran Turismo 1 Intro, still my favorite intro.    

For those who ask about the song:

Manic Street Preachers - Everything must Go (Chemical Brothers Remix).

With the exception of the other GT games.   This game is still untouched by other racing games.
